dct_title_s: Archiepiscopatus Maghdeburgensis, et Anhaltinus Ducatus : cum terris adjacentibus
dct_description_sm: Map of the archdiocese of Magdeburg, now part of the Magdeburg district, and the former Duchy of Anhalt, now part of the Magdeburg and Halle districts. Relief shown pictorially. Latin text on verso with caption title: Archiepiscopatus Magdeburgensis, cum terris adjacentibus; p. 26; signature Bb. From: Theatrum orbis terrarum, sive Atlas novus ... / editae a Guiljel. et Ioanne Blaeu. Amsterdami : Apud Iohannum Guiljelmi F. Blaeu, 1644-1645.
